          <text>
                    <body>
                              <pb n="1"/>
                              <p rend="align(right)">
                                        <placeName>Richmond</placeName>
                                        <date>March 1849</date>
                              </p>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Mr Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(2)">Sir yours of the inst. I duly received<lb/> with
                                        the package by the express, Since writing<lb/> I have
                                        obtained another subscriber <persName>Isaac
                                                  Leriner</persName><lb/> the persons you mention in
                                        your letter for me<lb/> to call on I have done so, but they
                                        will not<lb/> subscribe. I shall endeavour to obtain as
                                        many<lb/> as I can but I am afraid that they will not<lb/>
                                        be many as the people of this city are very slow<lb/> in
                                        subscribing, I think you had better send<lb/> say 20 or 25
                                        numbers of the Vol 7 I will<lb/> give the first number away
                                        gratas &amp; call<lb/> on those that I give them to they
                                        may<lb/> some of them subscribe by so doing, I have<lb/>
                                        received from <persName>Jacob Ezekiel</persName> the
                                        following books<lb/> which I have subject to your order</p>
                              <p>Catechism 30, <sic>Sprit</sic> of <sic>Judeasm</sic> 6, Jewish
                                        faith 2,<lb/> spelling book 5, daily Prayers 3 vol, Daily
                                        Prayer 3 sets<lb/> 2 paper 1 full bound, school teacher
                                        assistant 1,<lb/> discourses on the jewish religion 4 full bound,<lb/>
                                        <sic>Pentatuech</sic> 2 sets full bound 1 set paper,
                                        Occident<lb/> 59 No of Vol first from No 1 to 10, 72 No
                                        of<lb/> vol third from No 1 to 12, 83 No Vol 4 from<lb/> No
                                        1 to 12, 51 No Vol 5 No 1 to 12, 43 No<lb/> Vol second No 1
                                        to 12, he says he has some<lb/> more sets of Books which he
                                        would</p>
                              <pb n="2"/>
                              <p>hand over to me in case you write to him you<lb/> can request him
                                        to give me all books &amp; other<lb/> articles belonging to
                                        you if you think proper to<lb/> do so, I will attend to your
                                        business is it<lb/> should be attended to &amp; use all
                                        endeavours to<lb/> obtain subscribers I am in hopes to
                                        obtain<lb/> a goodly number of subscribers, you will<lb/>
                                        please when you write to me write<lb/> more plain as I found
                                        it difficult<lb/> to make out your writing in hopes<lb/>
                                        that this will find you in the enjoyment<lb/> of good health
                                        I remain yours</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">Resptly</p>
                              <p rend="indent(10)">
                                        <persName role="author">N Ezekiel</persName>
                              </p>
                              <p>you will please let me know if you paid<lb/> for the package as the
                                        bill has been sent<lb/> to me &amp; I declined paying
                                                  <sic>untill</sic> I hear<lb/> from you, in case
                                        you prepaid send<lb/> the receipt to me <persName
                                                  role="author">N Ezekiel</persName></p>
                              <pb n="3"/>
                              <p>
                                        <addressee>Revd. Isaac Leeser</addressee>
                              </p>
                              <p rend="indent(1)">
                                        <placeName>
                                                  <hi rend="underline">Philadelphia</hi>
                                        </placeName>
                              </p>
                    </body>
